    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "Your letter dated October 27, 1954, with",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "enclosures, has just been received.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "The thought prompting your writing me is",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "very much appreciated, and I was interested in look-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "ing over the cuttings you forwarded.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "Since your communication may be of concern",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "to another governmental agency, I am taking the liberty",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "of forwarding a copy of it and copies of the two arti-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "cles you noted to the Director, Office of Special In-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "vestigations, The Inspector General, Department of the",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "Air Force, The Pentagon, Washington 25, D. C.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "I want to take this occasion to thank you",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "for your kind expression of good wishes. I hope that",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "my efforts will continue to merit your esteem.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "Sincerely yours,",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
